				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/B%E1%BA%A7n-s%C4%A9-ng%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-NkPTPfZHXaMUN49RaMEEhg">Bần sĩ ngâm kỳ 2 - 貧士吟其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-D%E1%BA%A7n/author-xraflgHOfFZLZePKI11Alg">Đường Dần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/H%C3%A0n-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-ozIfpNSyzUEvpymmWeLyZQ">Hàn đường - 寒塘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C6%B0-Kh%C3%B4ng-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-mmPw1MZmtgbKEg6cv2Vw1A">Tư Không Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/H%C3%A0nh-dinh-th%C3%B9-L%C3%A3-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1/poem-6p-EAOfKVDn-XAwNeJW1ZA">Hành dinh thù Lã thị ngự - 行營酬呂侍御</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Khanh/author-tOqeEdGQ0OZRwfU1Vi35GA">Lưu Trường Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/Kh%C3%A1ch-Nh%E1%BA%A1n-M%C3%B4n-t%C3%A1c/poem-o2H5bxyd5PFYnfzhWibSuQ">Khách Nhạn Môn tác - 客雁門作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Qu%C3%A2n/author-Uj_DhxmeC-SDbSqFUZOc6w">Khuất Đại Quân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Long-C%C6%A1/Qu%E1%BB%B7-l%E1%BB%97i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QNij4oLcYqqR3c_w1oTavw">Quỷ lỗi ngâm - 傀儡吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Long-C%C6%A1/author-LP68Aop4_S5Jf74CeC8Mjg">Lý Long Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Hu%E1%BB%91ng/Quy-s%C6%A1n-t%C3%A1c/poem-FoVNpd1kGzrHUaJJkwXWxQ">Quy sơn tác - 歸山作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91-Hu%E1%BB%91ng/author-s27cAGHwrATcau0Gm-2RLQ">Cố Huống</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/S%C6%A1n-th%C3%B4n-c%E1%BA%A3m-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-v6_CQ6TsQFBYRt0-vHeBmA">Sơn thôn cảm hứng - 山村感興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-dW12UVYh-vPxg4IlKpEmEA">Tích biệt hành, tống Lưu bộc xạ phán quan - 惜別行送劉僕射判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-khoa-vi%C3%AAn-lai-th%C3%A1m/poem-QM0YgOaVAy9gYINLz7ljiw">Trần khoa viên lai thám - 陳科員來探</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/Xu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%8Bch-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i/poem-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Xuân tịch lữ hoài - 春夕旅懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BB%93/author-kzRUGlov9gv6H-eBsn_tAA">Thôi Đồ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
